{"tid":1788931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想多謝尋晚73A幫我俾車錢嘅女人","createTime":"2019-12-19T05:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T05:48:48.000Z","uid":279632,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fba530ce6900c6c38327ad7cc6baea430caaf875","tid":1788931,"uid":279632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"(借朋友acc 開 po)<br />\n<br />\n話說尋晚上咗巴士後發現自己八達通負咗錢<br />\n程車要$10.3<br />\n自己身上得張廿蚊同綠卡...<br />\n咁我唯有同車上嘅人唱錢，但佢地話冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知依個時候有個好好人嘅女人<br />\n走上前話幫我俾 <br />\n佢嘟咗佢張八達通之後<br />\n我同佢講同你唱番錢吖<br />\n佢話唔駛，就落咗車<br />\n一句多謝都嚟唔切講...<br />\n嗰下個人呆咗，覺得唔好意思<br />\n但係又好感動<br />\n喺無助嘅時候有人幫自己嘅感覺真係好溫暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我估佢係見我學生所以幫我俾住先<br />\n<br />\n如果幫我嗰位絲打見到依個po嘅<br />\n小妹想喺到同你講番聲多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abec798dce90d761687f208b01ef741417e62cd","tid":1788931,"uid":1891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n毋忘元朗恐襲事件<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SDdw0Ke.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDdw0Ke.jpg&h=23920099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RRKyxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RRKyxN.jpg&h=fcfe2918&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wrd5kKm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrd5kKm.jpg&h=81977b54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb35bd1942e34f369b63d0525679518da9f3a835","tid":1788931,"uid":206253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦 少少錢  <br />\n我欣賞你冇用到綠卡<br />\n如果下次有人都係咁 你幫返佢就得啦"},{"pid":"b4cb83c4da504826e5406e9b174e1f52ff04e98a","tid":1788931,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike"